---
import SectionHeading from './SectionHeading.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="reveal">
  <div class="container">
    <SectionHeading title="About" />
    <div class="about-content">
      <p class="about-hook">
        I'm a Sarajevo-based software engineer focused on backend and platform engineering —
        .NET, SQL, cloud-native services, and real-time systems. Over 6+ years I've modernized
        legacy .NET estates, designed event-sourced microservices, and cut page loads from
        15s to 3s in production. My focus is systems teams can actually operate: maintainable,
        observable, and ready to scale.
      </p>
      <ul class="about-bullets">
        <li>
          <strong>Cross-domain delivery</strong> — modernizations, real-time applications, and architecture-heavy projects across web, desktop, and cloud.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Clean Architecture, DDD, and TDD</strong> — modular monoliths and event-sourced microservices with high test coverage from day one.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>AI-assisted engineering workflows</strong> — I design agent orchestration, reusable skills, and human review gates to accelerate delivery while preserving quality.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-content {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-hook {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .about-bullets {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .about-bullets li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .about-bullets li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.6em;
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .about-bullets strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
